@LicenseManager.API_HostAddress = https://localhost:7223
@accessToken = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@refreshToken = PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Login and copy accessToken/refreshToken from the response
POST {{LicenseManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "support@metronux.com",
  "password": "admin@123"
}

### 2. Generate encrypted license for a pending subscription
POST {{LicenseManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/license/generate?subscriptionId=1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3. Download encrypted .lic file for a pending subscription
GET {{LicenseManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/license/download?subscriptionId=1
Accept: application/octet-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. Verify encrypted license text by paste
POST {{LicenseManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/license/verify-license
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "licenseDocument": "PASTE_THE_ENCRYPTED_LIC_CONTENT_HERE"
}

### 5. Verify encrypted .lic file by upload
POST {{LicenseManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/license/verify-file
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="licenseFile"; filename="subscription-1.lic"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

PASTE_FILE_CONTENT_HERE
--boundary--

### 6. Activate encrypted license by paste
POST {{LicenseManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/license/activate
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "licenseKey": "PASTE_THE_ENCRYPTED_LIC_CONTENT_HERE",
  "machineId": "MACHINE-001",
  "hostname": "EMS-SERVER",
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.10"
}

### 7. Refresh token using current access token and refresh token
POST {{LicenseManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 8. Logout using current access token and refresh token
POST {{LicenseManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}
